<p>英 /dɪ'preʃn/    美 /dɪ'preʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1c-u">1.<strong>[C] &amp; [U] 沮丧；消沉；抑郁 (症)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>get into a state of depression 
变得消沉/抑郁</p></div>

<h4 id="2c">2.<strong>[C] 不景气；萧条期：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His family business was ruined in the Great Depression of the early l930s.  
他的家族企业毁于20世纪30年代初期的经济大萧条。</p><footer>2011 山东</footer></div></div>